You may be put on bed rest if it is preeclampsia.

Yes sounds like pre eclampsia.  I'm 38 weeks and starting to get the symptoms, but I don't have protein in my urine yet. If it is pre eclampsia I think the only way to cure it is to deliver, but they will keep a close eye on you.
